title: ash meltdown
description:
Fourth studio album from Northern Irish indie rock veterans follows 2001&#039;s &#039;Free All Angels&#039; and showcases a shockingly heavy new sound. Inspired by protests against the war in Iraq, Tim Wheeler has penned a set of thunderous, metallic rock tunes which nevertheless retain the classic poppy, melodic Ash sound. Includes the singles &#039;Orpheus&#039; and &#039;Clones&#039; which was available only as a download
